text: Mariyu vastavaniki memu israyil santati variki undataniki manci sthananni icci, variki uttama jivanopadhini prasadincamu. Mariyu vari vaddaku divyajnanam vaccinanta varaku vari madhya bhedabhiprayalu raledu. Niscayanga, ni prabhuvu punarut'thana dinamuna vari madhya unna bhedabhiprayalanu gurinci tirpu cestadu
